close_reason: "Published consolidated governance refactor report with before-after metrics, validation outcomes, and residual follow-up issue links."
body: "Report scope: baseline vs final counts, hierarchy integrity remediation, duplicate-cluster consolidation mappings, metadata enrichment outcomes, validation sweep status, and residual issue tracking links for remaining product-level warnings.\n\nBaseline snapshot: items=464 before new follow-ups; metadata warnings close_reason_missing=83 estimate_missing=1; hierarchy anomalies self_parent=212 and missing_parent_non_epic=2.\\n\\nExecution outcomes: hierarchy repairs=214+1 anomaly fix; duplicate clusters consolidated=9 with 31 superseded mappings; metadata contextualization updates applied across all items; closed missing close_reason reduced to 0; missing estimated_minutes reduced to 0.\\n\\nFinal snapshot: items=467 after report creation (Epic=49 Feature=77 Task=266 Issue=28 Chore=47); status mix open=3 in_progress=1 blocked=4 closed=450 canceled=9.\\n\\nValidation status: metadata/resolution/history_drift/command_references all clean. Residual warning: validate_files_missing_linked_paths:9 is tracked as follow-up issue pm-m9tv. Future improvement feature: pm-7lum for duplicate-cluster automation/reporting.\n\nFinal post-close correction: current tracker totals are items=467 with status mix open=3 blocked=4 closed=451 canceled=9 (in_progress=0). Full validate sweep is clean for metadata/resolution/history_drift/command_references; only validate --check-files residual warning remains and is tracked by pm-m9tv."
